{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"900e70846b","title":"给张仙朋的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3807dad12b","index":0,"year":1961,"month":12,"day":24,"articleId":"900e70846b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"41def0a3c5","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周世钊，当时任湖南省副省长。"},{"id":"e63007c0d5","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见谭用之《秋宿湘江遇雨》（《全唐诗》卷七百六十四），下句原为“暮雨千家薛荔村”。"},{"id":"897fed6c85","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是湖南长沙岳麓山云麓宫望湘亭上的一副对联，录自清末诗人黄道让的七律《重登岳麓》（《雪竹楼诗稿》卷六），上句原为“西南云气开衡岳”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"1c11db1c06","type":"title","text":"给周世卸的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b"},{"id":"41def0a3c5","type":"paragraph","text":"世钉同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b"},{"id":"e63007c0d5","type":"paragraph","text":"惠书收到，退复为歉。很赞成你的意见。你努力奋斗吧。我甚好，无病，堪以告感。秋风万里芙蓉国，暮雨朝云薛荔村。西南云气来衡岳，日夜江声下洞庭。同志，你处在这样的环境中，当不妙哉？","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b"},{"id":"897fed6c85","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b"},{"id":"5108135ae0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六一年十二月二十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b"}],"page":{"id":"288769a60d","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"900e70846b","start":499,"end":499}}}},"__N_SSG":true}